&#9;For custom rendering, you will need @SG_ML_L017015SG - RI ⁽㈳㈴㈳㈮㈱㈨㈠㈫ ㈧㈤㈱㈤⁾../tutorials/renderer. You can write custom shaders and send stuff to the GPU in a very simple way. The @SG_ML_L01101DSGRRendererWidget../cppclass/sgrrendererwidget is not interactive, so you need a transparent UI element on top of it for interactivity.
